<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573407' id='t-573407'>like the sluggers do, which is what all the expensive teams like the Yankees like to --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='578176' id='t-578176'>they like to pick up those guys.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='579516' id='t-579516'>This kid told him, you know, you gotta watch the guys, and you gotta go out and find</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584105' id='t-584105'>the guys who like to walk,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='585344' id='t-585344'>because getting on base by a walk</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587048' id='t-587048'>is just as good, and in our healthcare
system</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='589816' id='t-589816'>we need to figure out,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='591256' id='t-591256'>is that really a good pitch</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592832' id='t-592832'>or should we let it go by and not swing at everything?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595750' id='t-595750'>Thanks.</span>
</span>
</p>
